         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <userestrict id="aspace_d17da46051cdb5ea734c44c9b1e95aa3">
         <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
         <p>Copyright has not been transferred to Yale University.</p>  
      </userestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_5aee828a1447bcaeb4c0abb9aa57d4d3">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Collection of Leather Bookplates, Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library, Yale University.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_634fe4598d3fac3333dd20cc99591219">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection contains leather bookplates, including both standard bookplates as well as supralibros, or super ex-libris, which are marks of ownership typically stamped on the exterior cover of a book.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_968f7ed11d7fb523ff1150c29b04c311">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into two series: I. Bookplates – Leather. II. Correspondence and Ephemera.</p>  
      </arrangement>
